<F P=102>  MB1803132994 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 1100 GMT 18 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB1803132994 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The ANC [African National Congress] has not been 
informed about a new initiative concerning the IFP's [Inkatha 
Freedom Party] participation in the election as mentioned by 
State President de Klerk. ANC spokesman Cyril Ramaphosa said at 
a news conference in Johannesburg that he interpreted Mr. de 
