<F P=104>  Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] General Constand Viljoen's Freedom Front has 
announced their candidate list for the April election. There 
were no surprises at the media conference in Pretoria today. 
Topping their national list is General Constand Viljoen, 
followed by Dr. Pieter Mulder, Dr. Corne Mulder, Mr. Willem 
