Werth is number eight, and CP [Orange] Free State leader Abrie 
Oosthuizen number 10. Number 14 on the national list is former 
Afrikaner Volksunie [Afrikaner National Union] member Moolman 
Mentz. Thirty-one nominees appear on the Freedom Front's 
