<H3> <TI>   ANC Official: Agreement Reached on Volkstaat </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB1903064394 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 0500 GMT 19 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB1903064394 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The national chairman of the ANC [African National 
Congress], Mr. Thabo Mbeki, says an agreement has been reached 
with the Freedom Front on a volkstaat [homeland]. Addressing 
businessmen at Richard's Bay. Mr. Mbeki said the ANC would be 
