<H3> <TI>   Cabinet Meets, Discusses Security Problems </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  EA2203210094 Bujumbura Radio-Television Nationale du Burundi 
Radio in French 1800 GMT 22 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA2203210094 </F>
<F P=104>  Bujumbura Radio-Television Nationale du Burundi 
