<H3> <TI>   Bomb Explosion Reported Near Border With Ghana </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AB2203160194 London BBC World Service in English 1515 GMT 22 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AB2203160194 </F>
<F P=104>  London BBC World Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Focus on Africa" program] </F>
  [Text] A powerful bomb explosion at dawn today completely 
razed to the ground premises of a popular drinking bar, Ataaso, 
in Lome only a few meters from the Togo-Ghana border. The bomb 
blast did a lot of damage to property and shook the adjacent 
houses to their very foundation, raising the specter of a bomb 
scare among the population. 

</TEXT>

